snippet.title: #17 Circus - VC 4000
snippet.description: A short sample from game #17 for Interton. This game is a Complete rip off - of Circus Atari released about one year earlier. However the powerfull videochip in the VC 4000 makes this an enjoyable game. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2013/04/17-circus-vc-4000.html
